item.description:
Play Cribbage!

Come out, meet new people, have dinner and play some cards. We have been playing every other Tuesday since the spring and would like to have some new players join us.

We meet at 6:00 and play until 8 or 9. Dinner is optional and you may arrive late.

We meet at skellig's, which has good, reasonably priced food and around 8 or 9 there is live acoustic music.

Park in the municpal lot beind Skellig's, entrance off of Pine St, free after 6.
item.name: Cribbage, Tuesday October 23, 2007
